17:10.507 --> 17:12.031
which was wrong.

17:12.117 --> 17:13.771
I totally get it.

17:13.858 --> 17:14.771
[laughs]

17:14.858 --> 17:16.512
I'’m sorry.

17:16.599 --> 17:18.906
Thank you.

17:18.993 --> 17:20.778
And I'’m sorry.

17:20.865 --> 17:22.432
What are you sorry about?

17:22.519 --> 17:24.521
I don'’t know.

17:24.608 --> 17:27.436
I'’m just more comfortable
being the one who apologizes.

17:27.523 --> 17:28.960
[chuckling]

17:31.267 --> 17:32.747
[sighs]

17:32.834 --> 17:33.922
So how are you doing?

17:35.054 --> 17:36.620
Better than I was.

17:36.707 --> 17:39.623
That'’s good to hear.

17:39.710 --> 17:40.929
So what were the four of you

17:41.016 --> 17:42.235
