17:43.540 --> 17:44.802
Canada?

17:44.889 --> 17:47.109
Yeah, I follow Jill
on Instagram.

17:47.196 --> 17:49.024
There was a whole bunch
of pictures of your trip.

17:49.111 --> 17:52.201
Oh, yeah...

17:52.288 --> 17:55.074
We just decided, you know,

17:55.161 --> 17:56.858
spur of the moment,
to hit the road

17:56.945 --> 17:58.033
process and heal...

17:59.643 --> 18:01.471
You could almost
call it sort of a...

18:01.558 --> 18:03.082
spiritual retreat.

18:03.169 --> 18:04.126
Christy!

